Run tests:
UI smoke: npx playwright test tests/ui --grep "@smoke"
API tests: npx playwright test tests/api
All tests: npx playwright test
View reports: npx playwright show-report

Direct CLI â†’ npx playwright test tests/ui --grep "@smoke"
Via npm script â†’ npm run test:smoke



